tip.text: Have your coffee outside on the veranda after lunch, as part of your buffet!
Take the new tollway from Colombo and you could be here in 1 hr!
Crabs are really expensive! Rs. 6000 for a crab - now I really need to go to Hospital...
Tea is really expensive and less than ordinary... Rs. 300 for Tea bag tea!
Reserve your table Way in advance; They only have crabs for now, so no fish - hope they change that soon!
